lyrics:
Ka lungchhia hi man pek kha hriain,
Hlim takin a lo lawm fo thin;
Pathian thu pek mawi leh a hmuhin;
Mi sual chhandam a hmuh pawhin;
Nunna petu chu an tithi a,
Thawhlehna ropui chu an phum;
Chatuanin remna a lo ni a,
Chungnung berin mihring a hum.

Kalvari tlangah a lo tuar a,
Mi sualte kara a awm khan;
Sawisatu thate a tichak a,
Amah thing lera khenbeh nan;
Mi sualte leiba a pek laia,
A Pa thupek tihmawi khan;
Pathian felna a lo eng mawi a,
Khawngaih remnaah ka lo thiam.

Lalber leh Remtu ruang an phumin,
Ka thla, chu mi chu ngaihtuah la;
Amahah leilung a her laiin,
Leilungah amah an zalh a;
Angel-ho fak ber a ingaitlawm,
Boral tawh fate chhandam nan;
Tunah hian mawi leh berin a awm,
Lei mi zawng zawngin fak ila.
